tyson-draws-stuff-the-art-of-kirk-brillo.title: Tyson Draws Stuff - The Art of Kirk Brillon
tyson-draws-stuff-the-art-of-kirk-brillo.description: I have made it. My first art book. This book was created with the help of a successful Kickstarter campaign. Thanks everyone for that. :)2019 has been an incredible artistic journey for myself and I wanted to encapsulate it in a book. It will provide you with 100 pages in glorious colour featuring my art and some of my short stories based on that same artwork.  Along this journey I have learnt a lot of things. I thought it was time to pass along this information to anyone seeking to make art out of chaos. I can’t be the only one out there seeking to create in this way as I’ve seen some others out there doing the same things before me. The information from those before me has been relatively hard to find, so I guess it is up to me to help others struggling with their art.There are two versions of the book available. A softcover version with a beautiful full colour cover and the limited addition hardcover. The hard cover is a limited numbered run bound in a laser etched faux leather cover. This will be a great coffee table book are a lovely addition to any collection.Book is now shipping.
